Breakpoint        Class infix        Dimensions
Extra small       (default)           < 576px
Small               sm                >= 576px
Medium              md                >= 768px
Large               lg                >= 992px
Extra large         xl                >= 1200px
Extra extra large   xxl               >= 1400px


Modifiers
In this line, <div class="alert alert-primary" role="alert">, the '-primary' part is the modifier.
There are 8 modifiers, primary, secondary, success, info, warning, danger, light, dark.
